{"tid":1817444,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"45歲李思捷登陸抖音唱歌跳舞派飛吻　微博網民︰那個吻有點油膩","createTime":"2020-01-09T05:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T10:09:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":395,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"352f4b6df5b117f9673e98e0ab7937ef3b618248","tid":1817444,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:46:28.000Z","msg":"近年愈多愈多網民玩內地短視頻App「抖音」，這個應用程式佔領年輕網路族群，原來連香港的藝人也不例外，例如高海寧﹑林夏薇和鄧佩儀等等，他們都有開抖音帳號拍片，日前藝人李思捷也開通了帳號，拍第一條片和粉絲Say Hi。<br />\n<br />\n現年45歲的李思捷相當緊貼潮流，開設了抖音帳號，短短3天就吸了10萬粉絲，暫時有兩條片，第一條片是跟網民們Say Hi，片中李思捷繼續用他驚人的模仿能力扮「四大天王」&mdash;&mdash;張學友、劉德華、郭富城和黎明唱歌，歌詞Crossover了他們四人的名曲歌名，唱完後，李思捷以不太純熟的普通話跟網民打招呼，說到︰「大家好，我是李思捷，新年快樂，從今天開始，我會經常在抖音和大家見面，新的一年，生活會有更多精彩，我們一起期待。」片尾還動了一動跳了幾下，載歌載舞，又送上飛吻，看來對粉絲好熱情！<br />\n<br />\n李思捷又在微博上載同一段片段，寫道︰「我開了抖音，你會做我的粉絲嗎？」微博網民似乎就非常喜歡，紛紛留言︰「思捷好開心的樣子啊！見到你再次出現，我們都好開心呢！」﹑「哇哇哇！立刻去關注！」﹑「感覺像20年前的李，年輕了！」還有人希望他可以上內地綜藝，同時又有人搞笑的說︰「很期待，就是後面的那個吻有點油膩，下次注意，我只期待你的視頻，吻就不用了，謝謝。」看來也頗受內地網民的歡迎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3823262/org/4eb4691f36a2b3c91efbf5592180e313.jpg/h9-tLlwAou5r5TtV7lF_iTVoIv-B4a0nT5hjuU-YY7k?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3823262%2Forg%2F4eb4691f36a2b3c91efbf5592180e313.jpg%2Fh9-tLlwAou5r5TtV7lF_iTVoIv-B4a0nT5hjuU-YY7k%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=577ef1eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3823202/org/ed185732493b93a843f00b85266e0936.PNG/mbK-uQqu05odMzo60DjKt9WfRKjF9tvshPSWnoT0lp4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3823202%2Forg%2Fed185732493b93a843f00b85266e0936.PNG%2FmbK-uQqu05odMzo60DjKt9WfRKjF9tvshPSWnoT0lp4&h=28fa5d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3823033/org/a3d54c2c5313596736f20f86a2b78a36.PNG/nWYHY19RKr5qKWL4ssVTGeClTue3Bb4pJrkV9ya5Ffc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3823033%2Forg%2Fa3d54c2c5313596736f20f86a2b78a36.PNG%2FnWYHY19RKr5qKWL4ssVTGeClTue3Bb4pJrkV9ya5Ffc&h=4df31f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource: 支那01"},{"pid":"3fc0113e2abb0394b6910af771393961d10c89ff","tid":1817444,"uid":132587,"like":370,"dislike":3,"score":367,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:48:37.000Z","msg":"當支那人都拒你於千里 可想言之佢連垃圾都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de04cf20749728f9aabda7a95a69e4c2e4ecfc9f","tid":1817444,"uid":2419,"like":373,"dislike":0,"score":373,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾做左十幾廿年仲係扮緊四大天王<br />\n<br />\n仲以為自己懷才不遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895d395252dffb3363881352cb1e98de1d6a8291","tid":1817444,"uid":81355,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:02:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全世界埋位</strong></span>"},{"pid":"477fa381b35bc3d74775a4626a63cb5e0eb31ccf","tid":1817444,"uid":261849,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:06:15.000Z","msg":"又唔係好睇佢做個D劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c62b3ecb05e7d482cc5ddeca27ea3c3fd2db28f","tid":1817444,"uid":3747,"like":100,"dislike":1,"score":99,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:07:17.000Z","msg":"現年45歲的李思捷相當緊貼潮流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91437e5ef4974dc574fae1b703d114d66d1dc8a3","tid":1817444,"uid":18895,"like":93,"dislike":2,"score":91,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:08:04.000Z","msg":"仲係扮4大天王又唔係似"},{"pid":"e9b4eaf500b3fce95549b9013687fb6d25436379","tid":1817444,"uid":158977,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T06:08:19.0